_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasOutput> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasOutput> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
