# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#hasSpatialPart
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasSpatialPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
