<https://w3id.org/pink#hasSpatialPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A proper part of a whole, whose parts always cover the full temporal extension of the whole within a spatial interval."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasSpatialPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "hasSpatialPart"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasSpatialPart> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "The part is connected with the rest item or members with hasContact relations only (no hasNext)."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#hasTemporalPart
<https://w3id.org/pink#hasTemporalPart> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
