<https://w3id.org/pink#nonOverlaps> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#propertyDisjointWith> <https://w3id.org/pink#overlaps> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#nonOverlaps> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The relation between two individuals that does not share any parts."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#nonOverlaps> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "nonOverlaps"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#output
<https://w3id.org/pink#output> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#overlaps
<https://w3id.org/pink#overlaps> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#overlaps> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#SymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#overlaps> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ReflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#overlaps> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The relation between two individuals representing entities that share at least one of their parts."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#overlaps> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "overlaps"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo
<https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#isOvercrossedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relation an entity to an activity that it interacts with."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "participatesTo"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#participatesTo> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "The entity through overlaps the activity."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#priorRelease
<https://w3id.org/pink#priorRelease> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#priorRelease> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#causedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#priorRelease> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#priorRelease> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#priorRelease> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pink#Software> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#priorRelease> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/pink#Software> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#priorRelease> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Direct relation that relates a software to the most resent earlier release of the software."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#priorRelease> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "priorRelease"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#priorRelease> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Useful for tracking the provenance of software releases."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#processedFrom
<https://w3id.org/pink#processedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#processedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#isAfter> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#processedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#processedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#processedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Indirect relation that relates the output of an activity to its input."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#processedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "processedFrom"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#semiotical
<https://w3id.org/pink#semiotical> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#semiotical> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The base of all semiotic relations."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#semiotical> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "semiotical"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#semiotical> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Semiotic relations can be seen as shortcuts that replaces a series of complex causal relations with a single relation."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#semiotical> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Semiotic relations take part in a triadic semiotic meaning-making process, where an 'interpreter' connects a 'sign' (e.g. a property) to an entity (called 'referent')."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#semiotical> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "The semiotic relations in the PINK Annotation Scheme are inspirred by EMMO, which in turn is based on the semiotic theory by Charles Sanders Peirce (1839-1914)."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#ssbdDimension
<https://w3id.org/pink#ssbdDimension> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#ssbdDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/pink#SsbdDimension> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#ssbdDimension> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/usageNote> "One of `pink:functionality`, `pink:safety`, `pink:environmental_sustainability`, `pink:social_sustainability`"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#ssbdDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Note this class redefined in PR https://github.com/PINK-project/PINK-annotation-schema/pull/15"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#ssbdDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "ssbdDimension"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#standsFor
<https://w3id.org/pink#standsFor> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#standsFor> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#semiotical> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#standsFor> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pink#Sign> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#standsFor> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#standsFor> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Connects a sign (e.g. a property) to an entity (a 'referent')."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#standsFor> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "standsFor"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#tierLevel
<https://w3id.org/pink#tierLevel> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#tierLevel> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#tierLevel> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/pink#TierLevel> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#tierLevel> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/usageNote> "One of `pink:tierlevel1` (ideation/design), `pink:tierlevel2` (lab phase/development), `pink:tierlevel3` (up-scaling/production)"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#tierLevel> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relate an entity to an SSbD tier level."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#tierLevel> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "tierLevel"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#used
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#used> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#isOvercrossedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relates an activity to an entity that it used."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "For example, :baking :used :spoon, :egg, :oven ." .
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "used"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#used> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "The activity A proper overlaps the entity E, where the non-overlapping part of E causes A."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasAssociatedWith> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#isOvercrossedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Agent> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relates an activity to an agent that had some (unspecified) responsibility for the occurence of this activity."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "wasAssociatedWith"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAssociatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "The activity is through overlapped by the agent."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasAttributedTo> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#causedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Agent> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relates an entity to an agent via an activity that both the entity and agent participates to."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "wasAttributedTo"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasAttributedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "The activity is through overlapped by the agent and overcrossed by the entity."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#wasDerivedBy
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasDerivedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasDerivedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasDerivedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasDerivedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#processedFrom> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasDerivedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasDerivedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasDerivedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasDerivedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasDerivedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Indirect relation that relates the output entity of an activity to its input entity."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasDerivedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "wasDerivedBy"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasGeneratedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#isOvercrossedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Relates an entity to the activity it was generated from."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "wasGeneratedBy"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasGeneratedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "The activity A proper overlaps the entity E, where the non-overlapping part of E is caused by A."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#wasInformedBy
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasInformedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasInformedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasInformedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasInformedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#isAfter> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasInformedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasInformedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasInformedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasInformedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasInformedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A one-directional relation between an activity that affects the subject activity."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#wasInformedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "wasInformedBy"@en .
