_:genid2 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onProperty> <https://w3id.org/pink#hasPart> .
_:genid2 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Restriction> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#Dataset> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/usageNote> "A collection of (more than one) datum, published or curated by a single agent, and available for access or download in one or more representations."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#Dataset> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Encoded data made of more than one datum."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#Dataset> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Dataset"@en .
