<https://w3id.org/pink#DateData> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> <https://www.w3.org/TR/xmlschema11-2/#date> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#DateData> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A symbolic data representing date. Format: YYYY-MM-DD (followed by an optional time zone offset, e.g. +01:00 for Central Europe)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#DateData> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "DateData"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#DateTimeData
<https://w3id.org/pink#DateTimeData> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#DateTimeData> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#SymbolicData> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#DateTimeData> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> <https://www.w3.org/TR/xmlschema11-2/#dateTime> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#DateTimeData> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A symbolic data representing datetime. Format: YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ss (followed by an optional time zone offset, e.g. +01:00 for Central Europe)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#DateTimeData> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "DateTimeData"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#Datum
<https://w3id.org/pink#Datum> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#Datum> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#Data> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#Datum> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/usageNote> "Datum is the building block of datasets."@en .
