<https://w3id.org/pink#Datum> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Datum"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#Description
<https://w3id.org/pink#Description> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#Description> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#Sign> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#Description> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A collection of properties that depicts an object."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#Description> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Description"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#Description> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "A description is not atomic in the sense that it is made of more than one property."@en .
