<https://w3id.org/pink#Indicator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#Property> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#Indicator> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A metric or signal that provides information about the state of a system. It simplifies complex realities into measurable values that can guide decisions."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#Indicator> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "For a computation is an indicator a specific property/datum that is provided in the output."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#Indicator> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Indicator"@en .
# 
