<https://w3id.org/pink#Information> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "Luciano Floridi, Information - A Very Short Introduction, Oxford University Press (2010) ISBN: 9780199551378"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#Information> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Definition> "Data with meaning (semiotic sign)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pink#Information> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Information"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pink#IntData
<https://w3id.org/pink#IntData> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#IntData> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#LongData> .
