<https://w3id.org/pink#IntegerData> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pink#NumericalData> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#IntegerData> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> <https://www.w3.org/TR/xmlschema11-2/#integer> .
<https://w3id.org/pink#IntegerData> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A data representing an arbritrary sized integer number."@en .
